        </a>
      </div>

      <!-- 프리미엄 패키지 -->
      <div class="mxt-card" style="padding:36px;">
        <div style="font-size:13px;font-weight:700;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.4);letter-spacing:0.05em;margin-bottom:12px;">PREMIUM</div>
        <h3 style="font-size:24px;font-weight:900;margin-bottom:4px;">전담 올인원</h3>
        <div style="margin:20px 0 8px;">
          <span style="font-size:13px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.4);text-decoration:line-through;">홈페이지 890,000원~</span>
        </div>
        <div style="font-size:42px;font-weight:900;letter-spacing:-0.04em;color:#4ade80;">
          월 <span style="font-size:32px;">40만원~</span>
