  <div style="max-width:1100px;margin:0 auto;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;flex-wrap:gap;gap:24px;">
    <div>
      <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;margin-bottom:10px;">
        <span style="font-size:16px;font-weight:900;color:white;">메이저텍스</span>
        <span style="color:rgba(255,255,255,0.2);">×</span>
        <span style="font-size:16px;font-weight:900;color:#4ade80;">디어스</span>
      </div>
      <p style="font-size:12px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.25);line-height:1.7;">
        소상공인 세무기장 + 홈페이지 올인원 파트너십<br>
        Powered by <a href="https://designd.co.kr" style="color:rgba(0,168,89,0.7);text-decoration:none;">designd.co.kr</a>
      </p>
    </div>
    <div style="display:flex;gap:24px;">
      <a href="https://designd.co.kr" style="font-size:13px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.35);text-decoration:none;" onmouseover="this.style.color='white'" onmouseout="this.style.color='rgba(255,255,255,0.35)'">디어스 홈</a>
      <a href="https://designd.co.kr/privacy" style="font-size:13px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.35);text-decoration:none;" onmouseover="this.style.color='white'" onmouseout="this.style.color='rgba(255,255,255,0.35)'">개인정보처리방침</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
